snippet.textDisplay: For anyone thinking about boosting their vq a thing to note: the oil feed T is not npt. It's BSPT and extremely sensitive. Do not over tighten it or it will crack your oil pan or break off in your oil pan causing you to do what these guys did lol. It only needs to be hand tight.
